{"type": "article", "id": 8222, "title": "我们到底该如何衡量 Apple Watch 的成败？", "description": "这不是件容易的事", "date": "2015-04-10T10:54:02Z", "super_tag": "Asymco", "tags": [{"id": 2074, "name": "Asymco"}, {"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 2871, "name": "Apple Watch"}, {"id": 231, "name": "Apple"}], "category": 4, "author": 70528, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222049y8lNmhdB9WPwqY1A.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#CCCCCC;\"><a href=\"http://www.asymco.com/2015/04/06/how-will-we-measure-apples-watch-success/\" target=\"_blank\">本文</a>由 </span><span style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#CCCCCC;\">Horace Dediu 授权《好奇心日报》发布</span><br>\r\n</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">这绝不是一件容易的事情。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">首先，苹果公司不会公布 Apple Watch 的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">季度营业额或者（大致的）单品</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">销售额，因此</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">我们无法对产品销售情况进行准确评价</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。另外，Apple Watch 的定价范围</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">十分</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">广泛，因此</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">对于特定价位的该产品，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">分析师很难确定</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">其准确的市场</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">需求。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">但不公布数据也有一个</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">隐蔽</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的好处。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">所有的数据都是人创造出来的，它所揭示的结论受很多因素的影响，其中包括：具体的测试对象、进行测试的人员以及动机。然而</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">如果没有数据，就没有证据</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，同时也就使结论失去了公信力。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">换句话说，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">没有测试你就无法得出结论，但你又不能确定具体去测试什么。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">因此，分析师们</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">急需一种评价体系或者起码是观点来指导他们选择被测试对象</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">而这需要以</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">经验和优秀的理论</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">而基础</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，那我们究竟</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">应该</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">用什么标准来判断 Apple Watch 是否</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">取得</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">成功？</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:9.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:x-small;\">以下是一些建议：</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:9.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:x-small;\"> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;font-size:9.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">1.  语言。看看“Watch”是否成为了“Apple Watch”的代名词。“Phone”指的不仅仅是“智能手机”，还有所有移动电话、蜂窝电话</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">等等用于传播信息的媒介</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。这是一个很好的测试，因为语义的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">转换只有在具有广泛影响力的思想引导下才能完成。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">并且，这</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">很</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">可能是有意</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">为之</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">2.  </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">iPhone 的使用</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">频率出现明显可测量的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">减少。Apple Watc</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">h </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">旨在</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">将</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span>iPhone<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">的很多应用转移到这个平台上面，因此转变的越多</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">使用 iPhone 的时间必然会相应的变少</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。然而，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这些剩下的时间会为继续持有 iPhone 的人增添一份独一无二的价值</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span>这种此消彼长的场景也曾经出现在 PC 与移动设备的对决中。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">3.  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">大屏 iPhone<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的出现</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。随着人们从口袋中拿出 iPhone </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">次数的减少</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">在解决那些</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">Apple Watch </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">无力解决的问题时，大屏 iPhone 将会更加便捷与实用。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">4. </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">iPhone </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的销量出现远超预料的增长。这意味着</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\"> Android </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">用户选择该平台是为了使用它的“附带功能”。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">要注意的是，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这与之前说过的使用</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span>iPhone </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的频率降低相矛盾。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">5. </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">针对 Apple Watc</span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">h </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">开发的应用。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这将涉及数以百万计的创新人才，所以</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">很难</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">预测该</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">领域</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">的</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">发展</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">走向，不过智能手机就是通过解决大量就业来创造新的经济价值的，因此 </span></span><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\">Apple Watc</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">h 也理应如此</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">作为一个附加效果，围绕 </span></span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:Verdana;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">Apple Watch </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">可能会出现一个新兴的商业帝国（起码会出现很多大型企业）。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"font-family:verdana;\">6.  </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;\">更新换代</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">。</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这个产品的更新速度会有多快，幅度会有多大？像</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">耳机和 Apple TV </span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">这样的基础</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">配件</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">都应该有其相应的更新周期</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">，更智能的设备就</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">应该</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">更新得</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">更</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">快。更新周期的长短可以推测出苹果公司对这个平台的态度，</span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">而对于积极评价的用户，他们的观点也可以促进其更新</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:9.5pt;\">。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:9.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font:9.5pt/20.79px 宋体;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;font-size-adjust:none;font-stretch:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">这些建议都比较模糊，而其数据的指示</span><span style=\"text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:20.79px;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">意义并不是很强</span><span style=\"text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:20.79px;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">。但从很多方面上</span><span style=\"text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:20.79px;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">来看</span><span style=\"text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:20.79px;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">，</span><span style=\"text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:20.79px;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">这仍然</span><span style=\"font:9.5pt/20.79px 宋体;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;font-size-adjust:none;font-stretch:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">比起任何一份财务业绩数据更有意义。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;line-height:15.6pt;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:9.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:x-small;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font:9.5pt/20.79px 宋体;text-align:left;color:#000000;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;font-size-adjust:none;font-stretch:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"white-space:normal;margin-left:0px;\">\r\n\t关于作者：\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tHorace H. Dediu 是独立分析公司 Asymco 的创始人，专注于分析移动计算行业进化之路上的成功与失败。Dediu 的分析和评论被《纽约时报》、《金融时报》、彭博电视等媒体频频引用。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t除了 Asymco.com，Dediu 也在每周一期的播客 Critical Path 评论移动产业，并著有同名书籍。Dediu 之前在哈佛商学院的导师、《创新者的窘境》的作者克里斯藤森也是 Critical Path 的座上宾。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t翻译 钟舒婷\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}